布兰妮斯皮尔斯表示她“永远不会重返音乐界” https://www.nme.com/news/music/britney-spears-never-return-to-music-industry-3565309?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=britney-spears-never-return-to-music-industryEli Ordonez Thu, 04 Jan 2024 02:26:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3565309 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布兰妮·斯皮尔斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>继 Charli XCX 合作传闻后，这位歌手在 Instagram 上发布了消息</p><p>布兰妮<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/britney-spears-never-return-to-music-industry-3565309">·斯皮尔斯 (Britney Spears) 表示她“永远不会重返音乐界”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布兰妮·斯皮尔斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/britney-spears@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/britney-spears">布兰妮·斯皮尔斯</a>在社交媒体上的一篇新帖子中宣布，她“永远不会重返音乐界”。</p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/controlling-britney-spears-review-3056900"><b>“控制布兰妮斯皮尔斯”评论：有毒的监管回到显微镜下</b></a></li></ul><p>今天（1 月 3 日），这位“Baby One More Time”歌手在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C1p-tjPPn0T/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>上发布了一篇措辞强硬的帖子，回应了有关她未来音乐事业的谣言。</p><p>意大利巴洛克艺术家吉多·雷尼 (Guido Reni) 创作的 1631 年画作《带着施洗者圣约翰头像的莎乐美》的屏幕截图附有说明文字，布兰妮·斯皮尔斯 (Britney Spears) 写道：“所以我们很清楚，大多数新闻都是垃圾！！！ ”</p><p> “他们一直说我会随机找人制作一张新专辑，”她补充道。 “我永远不会再回到音乐界了！！！当我写作时，我是为了好玩而写，或者是为了别人而写！！！”然后，她向读过她最近的回忆录的粉丝们进行了磨练，声称她在过去两年里一直在为其他艺术家代笔。</p><p> “对于那些读过我的书的人来说，有很多关于我的事情是你不了解的，”她写道。 “过去两年我为别人写了 20 多首歌！！！我是一名代笔作家，老实说我很喜欢这样！！！”</p><p>最后，她面对有关她的回忆录未经她许可就被出版的说法。 “人们还说我的书在未经我批准的情况下就被非法发布，但这与事实相去甚远，”她总结道。 “这几天的新闻你看了吗？？？我是如此被爱和祝福！！！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C1p-tjPPn0T/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 6